excerpt.rendered:
DESCRIPTION
Vitakraft Oven Baked Crunchy Bites are fruity treats for rabbits, guinea pigs, and hamsters. Baked to a super crunchy texture, they help support small animals’ dental health and satisfy natural gnawing instincts. Cranberries, oranges, and whole grains come together to make these treats both delicious and nutritious.

Key Benefits:

Made with real cranberries, oranges, and whole grains
Baked, super crunchy texture
Satisfies animals’ natural gnawing instincts
Supports dental health
